IMF Urges Italy’s Government to Continue Pursuing Fiscal Consolidation

-- B y   B e n   L i v e s e y
-- 
2011-07-12T22:49:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/imf-urges-italy-s-government-to-continue-pursuing-fiscal-consolidation.html
The International Monetary Fund said
Italy is experiencing a “weak” recovery driven by exports and
urged the nation to continue pursuing fiscal consolidation. The
IMF sees Italy’s economy growing 1 percent in 2011, it said in
an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Livesey at 
 blivesey@bloomberg.net  